{"tid":600040,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"近五百萬部 Android 手機被預載惡意程式 受影響手機主要是中國品牌","createTime":"2018-03-21T03:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T06:55:14.000Z","uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76d5d860ddcd7fe6fbff5217a61469b83b28fe22","tid":600040,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2034287/近五百萬部%20Android%20手機被預載惡意程式%20受影響手機主要是中國品牌\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2034287%2F%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%94%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E9%83%A8%2520Android%2520%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%A0%90%E8%BC%89%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F%2520%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C&d=5gUHD5hnZIOw1Z4EuMo5TMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=4496599d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2034287/近五百萬部%20Android%20手機被預載惡意程式%20受影響手機主要是中國品牌</a><br />\n<br />\n以色列一間網絡資訊科技安全公司 Checkpoint 近日發現一款名為「RottenSys」的惡意程式已經感染了約 500 萬部 Android 手機，當中主要是在中國發售的品牌，而惡意程式竟然是在出廠時已經被預載在手機內。<br />\n<br />\n【相關新聞】勒索觸發危機 神經網絡保安方案<br />\n<br />\n【相關新聞】甜網咪亂睇！報告指每 4 個手機用戶有 1 人中招<br />\n<br />\n根據 Checkpoint 的調查報告，惡意程式「RottenSys」會偽裝成「系統 Wi-Fi 服務」，獲取儲存空間、下載等權限，讀取用戶手機資料及在背景下載程式，更會向用戶發送假通知，透過騰訊、百度等廣告平台顯示彈出式全頁廣告，透騙用戶點擊廣告，根據統計資料，「RottenSys」10 日會在用戶手機共彈出約 13,250,756 次廣告，當中有 548,822 次廣告點擊，估計可獲取 11.5 萬美金，約港幣 90 萬。"},{"pid":"68b2ebe18399a29e71cb64c78b5af07e0e849bfa","tid":600040,"uid":23677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">當中主要是在中國發售的品牌</span><br />\n<br />\n文不對題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909309866b3f6571c800c28129e14e45673a15c2","tid":600040,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68b2ebe18399a29e71cb64c78b5af07e0e849bfa","tid":600040,"uid":23677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">當中主要是在中國發售的品牌</span><br />\n<br />\n文不對題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:55:14.000Z","msg":"禁link入去睇內文"}]}